---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | bbrep">
  <section class="shell content prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Researcher-first program reputation</h1>
    <p>
      bbrep exists to make public VDP and BBP experiences easier to compare without
      relying on screenshots, private chat logs, or opaque scoring. The repository is
      the source of truth, pull requests are the audit trail, and the static site is
      only a readable projection of that data.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial model</h2>
    <p>
      Automation validates structure and obvious consistency. Humans still decide
      whether a program is legitimate, whether a review is useful, and whether the
      submission respects confidentiality and disclosure boundaries.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      Reviews are individual opinions from independent researchers. This project is
      not affiliated with any bug bounty platform or company. Companies and program
      owners may contest reviews by opening an Issue with evidence. Only public
      programs are accepted.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
